Orly Airport V 3.1     August  1996 
------------------

Changing world file name to FLT$ORLY31.WORLD
Adding a new FLT$KEYMAP.DAT file with availability of 14 viewpoints
Adding VORS & NDB (Agen, Gaillac, Toulouse Nord, Muret)
Adding Biarritz terrain, VOR and runway
Adding coast from Fuentarrabia to l'Adour (river)
Adding Biarritz 27 runway ramp and ILS
Adding new entry points at Cerny airfield
Adding Socoa Tower (near St Jean de Luz)
Adding Ste Barbe Hill (St Jean de Luz)
Adding St Jean de Luz harbour & lights
Adding Aircraft Carrier & Destroyers
Adding Hendaye, St Jean de Luz and Biarritz beach (with entry points)
Adding various ship entry points (Hendaye, Biarritz and St Jean de Luz)
Adding "Rocher de la Vierge" and "Cap St Andre" (Biarritz)
Adding "Pointe Ste Anne" near Hendaye
Adding two other build procedures to build sub-worlds (Cerny world
and Euskadi world).

