Changing world file name to FLT$ORLY30.WORLD
Adding Toulouse-Blagnac terrain
Adding Toulouse-Blagnac runways, ramps and ILS
Adding Ndbs geometry (picked up into FLT$FINLAND-NIGHT.WORLD)
Adding Puy de Dome (old volcano near Clermont-Ferrand)
Adding a dozen other volcanos around the Puy de Dome.
Adding Clermont-Ferrand city
Adding Clermont-Ferrand Airport
Adding Clermont-Ferrand Cathedral
Adding a new FLT$KEYMAP.DAT file with a tenth view point bound on PF2 KP0
Adding Blagnac 2 Terminal parking
Adding Toulouse VOR and Ndb's
Adding Blagnac and Colomiers cities
Adding Toulouse city
Adding la Garonne (river) from Muret (South) to Merville (North)

